"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10021910\">",
"      How is this drug best taken?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10021911\">",
"      What do I do if I miss a dose?",
