"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 555px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Oral contraceptive therapy decreases hair growth in hirsute women",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 535px; height: 341px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Changes in hair growth rates, determined by photography, in hirsute women treated with ethinyl estradiol 30 g and desogestrel 0.15 mg (left panel) or not treated (right panel). The rate of hair growth was stable in untreated women but slowed by about 25 percent with oral contraceptive therapy.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
